original_title: Sonic Youth - Gila Monster Jamboree - January 5, 1985
overview: A video documenting Sonic Youth's performance at the Gila Monster Jamboree. Taking place in a remote location in the Mojave Desert, this was the bands first ever show on the West Coast. The bill also included bands such as Meat Puppets, Red Kross and Psi-Com.
title: Sonic Youth - Gila Monster Jamboree - January 5, 1985
